#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Each year in the Wesnoth calendar is composed of 12 months. These are, in "
#| "order:\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Whitefire\n"
#| "Bleeding Moon\n"
#| "Scatterseed\n"
#| "Deeproot\n"
#| "Scryer’s Bloom\n"
#| "Thorntress\n"
#| "Summit Star\n"
